  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a Huge or smaller creature you can see ends its turn within 30 feet of you, you can use your reaction to magically force it to make a Strength saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failed save, you pull the creature up to a number of feet equal to 5 times your proficiency bonus directly to an unoccupied space. If you pull the target to a space within reach of you, you can make a melee weapon attack or unarmed strike against it as part of this reaction.</p><p>You can use this reaction a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses of it when you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 3rd level spell slot.</p>",
